# No redundant code

Read `AGENTS.md` at the repo root for full guidance.

**On every task:**

1. Search the codebase for existing helpers, services, components, and types before adding new ones.
2. Extend or parameterize existing code — do not copy-paste the same logic into another file.
3. When you replace or consolidate something, delete the old implementation in the same change.
4. Keep one source of truth per concern (formatting, validation, types, UI, API shaping).

**Never** leave two ways to do the same thing unless they are intentionally different — and document why.
